### Get connection by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/connection/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get API definition by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api-definition/5
Accept: application/json

###

### Get API test data by integration ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api-datos/integracion/5

###

### Get default model from ETL-CONFIG-LLM-MS
GET http://localhost:8000/default-model

###

### Register a single schema match
POST http://localhost:8000/schema-matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceField": "first_name",
  "targetField": "givenName",
  "confidence": 0.95,
  "integrationId": 1,
  "status": "PENDING"
}

###

### Register multiple schema matches at once
POST http://localhost:8000/schema-matches/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matches": [
    {
      "sourceField": "first_name",
      "targetField": "givenName",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "integrationId": 1
    },
    {
      "sourceField": "last_name",
      "targetField": "familyName",
      "confidence": 0.92,
      "integrationId": 1
    }
  ]
}

###

### Full integration processing (connection + APIs + data + model)
GET http://localhost:8000/process-integration/1

###

### Run matching: extract fields from both APIs, call LLM, register matches
POST http://localhost:8000/run-matching/1
